Class ProtocolHandlerChainImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.james.protocols.api.handler.AbstractProtocolHandlerChain
      • org.apache.james.protocols.api.handler.ProtocolHandlerChainImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<ProtocolHandler>, Collection<ProtocolHandler>, List<ProtocolHandler>, ProtocolHandlerChain
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    POP3ProtocolHandlerChain, SMTPProtocolHandlerChain

    public class ProtocolHandlerChainImpl
extends AbstractProtocolHandlerChain
implements List<ProtocolHandler>
    AbstractProtocolHandlerChain which is mutable till the wireExtensibleHandlers() is called. After that all operations which try to modify the instance will throw and UnsupportedOperationException
